  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Validate that circulating cell free fetal nucleic acid can be used to identify a direct
      marker for fetal aneuploidy, particularly fetal Down Syndrome (DS), that is better than
      surrogate markers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
