      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Subject is female

          -  Subject is pregnant

          -  Subject is high risk aneuploid patient undergoing genetic counseling, unltrasound
             screening, amniocentesis and/or CVS procedure

          -  Subject is willing to provide blood specimen

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subject is not pregnant

          -  Subject is not willing to provide blood specimen

          -  Subject is not haveing aneuploid screening
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
